## License Grant

Subject to the terms and conditions of this License, Licensor hereby grants you the right to copy, modify, create derivative works, redistribute, and make non-production use of the Licensed Work. The foregoing rights are effective on the date Licensor first distributes or otherwise makes the Licensed Work available to a third party.

Notwithstanding the above, you may not use the Licensed Work for a Competing Use or in excess of the Usage Limits. 

A "Competing Use" means to use the Licensed Work to:
(a) provide a commercial API gateway service to third parties;
(b) offer LLM tool management or integration services as a business;
(c) create any commercial service that substitutes for, or offers substantially similar functionality to, apifai;
(d) redistribute apifai as part of a competing software product or service.

"Usage Limits" means the Licensed Work may be used in production environments with a maximum of 5 active gateway instances per organization. A "gateway instance" is defined as a single deployed apifai backend service, regardless of load balancing or clustering configuration.

